esktop-nav5"><b>CAREEER TRANSITIONS</b></div></a><a href="contact.php"><div id="desktop-nav6"><b>CONTACT US<br></b></div></a></div></div><div id="nav-menu"><div id="menu-btn"><div id="nav-menu1">Menu</div><div id="nav-menu2"><img src="images/hamburger.png" style="width: 100%; height: auto;"></div></div><div id="mobile-nav"><a href="index.php"><div class="mobile-nav-btn"><b href="index.php">HOME</b></div></a><a href="athletes.php"><div class="mobile-nav-btn"><b>ATHLETES</b></div></a><a href="entrepreneurs.php"><div class="mobile-nav-btn"><b>ENTREPRENEURS</b></div></a><a href="young-men.php"><div class="mobile-nav-btn"><b>YOUNG MEN</b></div></a><a href="career-transitions.php"><div class="mobile-nav-btn"><b>CAREER TRANSITIONS</b></div></a><a href="contact.php"><div id="nav-menu9"><b href="contact.php">CONTACT US</b></div></a></div></div><div id="i26"><div class="h1-wrapper"><div class="h1">Athletes</div></div></div><div id="i29"><div id="i30"><div id="i31"><i>Become a champion in your sport and in your life!</i><br></div></div></div><div id="i32"><div id="i33"><div class="h1-wrapper"><div class="h1">What Factors Affect Sport Performance?</div></div><div id="i36">Contrary to popular belief, there are several factors that affect sport performance.</div><div id="i37">Notice in the diagram below that you, the athlete, are just one of the factors.</div><div id="i38"><img src="images/athlete-flow-chart.svg" style="width: 100%; height: auto;"></div><div id="i39">One phrase that you will hear us say all the time at Life-Changing Coaching is: <b>“It’s all connected.”</b> We help you figure out how those other factors are affecting how you perform in your sport. We then help you devise a plan to turn your challenges into opportunities to improve your sport performance.<br></div><div class="h1-wrapper"><div class="h1">What is Performance Coaching?</div></div><div id="i42"><div>Performance coaching is helping athletes develop the most important organ in their bodies, their BRAINS.</div><div><br></div><div>When Los Angeles Lakers’ basketball player Ron Artest credited mental skills coaching for some of his success on the court, many people were surprised. They had assumed his success was due to his phenomenal basketball skills. But his physical skills were only part of the story. Another part of the story was the invaluable mental skills training that he received. And he is not alone. Research shows that if two athletes have the same levels of physical skill and fitness, the athlete with the STRONGER MIND will always win.</div><div><br></div><div>Performance coaching (also known as mental skills coaching or sport psychology) help athletes consistently perform in the upper ranges of their capabilities and more thoroughly enjoy the sport performance process.</div></div><div class="h1-wrapper"><div id="i44">What are Mental Skills?</div></div><div id="i45"><div>Mental skills are those things that you do with your mind that work together with your body to help you achieve your athletic goals. Here is a list of the 10 most important mental skills that every athlete needs to develop to be successful in his or her sport:</div><div><ol><li>Confidence<br></li><li>Conscientiousness<br></li><li>Determination<br></li><li>Drive<br></li><li>Focus<br></li><li>Happiness<br></li><li>Intelligence<br></li><li>Passion<br></li><li>Perseverance<br></li><li>Resilience</li></ol></div><div>One of the first things you will do when you start working with us is take a mental skills assessment. This assessment will give us the information that we need to help you improve your performance and become the best athlete you can be.</div></div><div id="i46">We can help you! Contact us today!<br></div></div></div><div id="pre-footer"><div id="pre-footer0"><img src="images/ACSMMemberWebID.gif" style="width: 100%; height: auto;"></div></div><div id="footer"><div id="footer0">Copyright © <span class="year">2018</span> Life Changing Coaching. All Rights Reserved.</div></div></div><